Clients:
GET /clients/ - List all clients.
POST /clients/ - Create a new client.
GET /clients/<id>/ - Fetch client details and associated projects.
PUT/PATCH /clients/<id>/ - Update a client.
DELETE /clients/<id>/ - Delete a client.

Projects:
POST /clients/<id>/projects/ - Add a project to a client and assign users.
GET /projects/ - List projects assigned to the logged-in user.


